### [Psalms Chapter 146](../../../bib/kjv/psa146.htm#001.md)

[Psalms 146:4](../../../bib/kjv/psa146.htm#004.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_004">psa 146:4</span></span>

That day - As soon as ever he is dead. Thoughts - All his designs and
endeavours either for himself or for others.

[Psalms 146:6](../../../bib/kjv/psa146.htm#006.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_006">psa 146:6</span></span>

For ever - Both because he liveth for ever to fulfil his promises, and
because he is eternally faithful.

